Anyways, the Cliff golems always drop 1 star metal.  The quest is currently bugged in the form of the starmetal.  It says you split the starmetal ore with a hammer and chisel......well you split it but only get one piece of starmetal bits.   So you need to kill 2 cliff golems in order to do this.  Chrol and I reported this to the dev team but i doubt this is high priority with SoL out.  This quest never recieved the same kind of fix attention that the coldain ring quest did because of the difficulty most people shy away from it.  So if you have any questions about the quest feel free to talk to me in game.  If i am raiding i will probably just send you an email answer since some steps can be very detailed.<br>
<br>
also cliff golem  level 58,  30k hp's  hits like a @#%$,  myself, eeep, ksarn and another monk smoked Golem + like 2 dragoons at the same time hehe.<br>
